Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't get out because there's no door...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Because there's no door...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:08.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki... Yuki... Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.83,0:01:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Say something, Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Because there's no door...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.21,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,There is a door...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...for Tama to select...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Selection..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:15.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:21.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:30.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:41.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"No Trespassing"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:22.66,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be in big trouble if\Nthe person earlier finds out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But, we need to check the place out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.22,Main,,0,0,0,,So... pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, your tears... shine like gems...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:49.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be your LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.73,Main,,0,0,0,,LRIG to the greatest of Selectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:58.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But... my true desire was probably different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu's sorrow... dark... filth... pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I was born from those feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:16.21,Main,,0,0,0,,But... battling alongside you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:24.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You, Ru... came inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...and spread within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I felt... something very beautiful,\Nand precious filling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:44.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You showed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:46.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...what I truly desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,...Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! I don't want to hear your thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:57.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't like the way you're\Nmaking it sound like a farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:05:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would parting be painful for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, for me it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:11.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn about your\Nemotional farewells and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,The battle ends when an LRIG disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You girls lose by default.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Iona, or should I say, Yuki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,...are you still able to battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru and Yuki won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.13,Main,,0,0,0,,--Shiro!\N--Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.72,Main,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.22,Main,,0,0,0,,How did she get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Use Grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Make Tama and Yuki into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Me coming together as one\Nwith Tama will just taint her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki, you're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like the snow that shines under the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty... Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, who dreams of the summer sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:18.42,Main,,0,0,0,,...and Yuki, who loves the winter snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.17,Main,,0,0,0,,If Tama and Yuki come together as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...you'll be like the snow, falling in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Level 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why my name...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I really like Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I really like Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,And the person who created\Nthem both is you, Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I can't say that I like you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, everyone went\Nthrough a lot of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And even now, everyone is in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Some girls have lasting scars on\Ntheir bodies and in their minds, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you had a chance to become Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:26.78,Main,,0,0,0,,The true you is next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure if this wasn't how things were...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,If we didn't meet like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,...I would have really liked you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:46.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hearing that doesn't\Nmake me the least bit happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate... I hate how you used past tense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:53.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith! Black Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking, Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:10.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if Selector battles themselves are wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:17.12,Main,,0,0,0,,...it still is the one and only\Nwish coming from Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What a sad looking room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu! Summon Arc Energe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack with Laevateinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:19.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you calling her by that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.35,Main,,0,0,0,,How is that doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, aside from her lack of appetite...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.19,Main,,0,0,0,,So, is that girl back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:29.99,Main,,0,0,0,,--Not that it matters to me...\N--So did that eat dinner already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Make that take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Not that I care...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:41.75,Main,,0,0,0,,My name was never spoken\Nin such a caring tone before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:48.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to be\Nthe greatest Selector there is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.56,Main,,0,0,0,,One who selects...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I... didn't select anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that I didn't\Nwant to make a selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any selections to make...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:21.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't take everything away from everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I gave everyone an opportunity\Nto make a selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if they were crying, smiling, or angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,...at least they could select!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I was even denied that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:41.64,Main,,0,0,0,,The only thing that connects to the outside\Nis the sky seen from that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This room was Mayu's world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a chance to select--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:51.11,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you seal Tama away, Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you only allow Yuki\Nto participate in battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu hated the world outside the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...the world lit by light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But in reality, she sought and longed for\Nthe world outside more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why, just when\NMayu's life came to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,...she made a selection...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,With that, Tama awakened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Beyond the colors of black, and of white...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...was a world of many colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:36.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...where Tama, longing for light\Nthat Mayu held, was released to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:39.20,Main,,0,0,0,,No... No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.37,Main,,0,0,0,,No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not me... I wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:54.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Come see the world outside\Ntogether with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.84,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you say such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:56.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.64,Main,,0,0,0,,...already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Why... are you trying to\Nprotect the LRIG I created?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,No one... loved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.48,Main,,0,0,0,,No one called me by my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,No one embraced me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,If we didn't meet like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,...I would have really liked you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If we met...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...could things have changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,...was to become an unknown\Nexistence and perish here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted others to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to affect the lives of\Nothers with the life I lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,...that was hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:58.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to get to know\Nmore about you, Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,And not through hatred, or with bad feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess what color I selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.81,Main,,0,0,0,,The color Mayu selected?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith at Level 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...can control all colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,This move can be used only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,If you can guess what Mayu selected...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...you win, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Get it wrong, and Mayu wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.79,Main,,0,0,0,,This card... is Mayu's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The color Mayu selected...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it the color of dark, the hatred\Nshe had for the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:44.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, is it the color of light\Nthat sealed Tama away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Beyond the colors of black...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,...and of white...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...was a world of many colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:13.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't hold myself back any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:17.04,Main,,0,0,0,,...what color is this card?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,A world without colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That card...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,...is non-colored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.15,Main,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, executed without a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Noooo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I have nothing in my hand, and no Arts to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:07.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu can't do anything in the next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Non-colored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,A color that erases all and\Nmarks the end of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:22.77,Main,,0,0,0,,And, it's a color that marks\Nthe beginning of everything, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It can be colored any way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu, you're going to set the colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...can begin again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,...can be embraced by someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:31.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's take our oath\Nbefore this world disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:34.97,Main,,0,0,0,,This time, let's make your wish come true, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It was to return the girls who became\NLRIG cards back to their original selves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:49.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn the girls who became LRIGs into humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,That would make you return back\Nto your original form, Mayu, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:18:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...it may turn Tama and Yuki into humans, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, you're like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru... you do understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Making a selection means to\Nselect one thing, not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I did make a selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to make a selection\Nat the sacrifice of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if that brings hardships, sorrow, or times\Nwhere I may cry, I'll still select everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the selection I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You really are a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking, Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...a new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like that building's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess things didn't disappear\Neven after the pillar fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:33.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, why are you so dressed up?\NYou have plans with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup! We're studying for our school exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I won't be out too late today, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ou...ch...\N--Wha...?! Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotta hand it to piggy-Ru. That hit hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're going to sleep,\Nsleep in bed or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Be careful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:02.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like Ru-{\i1}chan {\i0}grew, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Why yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,She's grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it! My brain can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only been an hour, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're planning to go to the same school\Nas Hitoe, you'll have to do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...gimme some of your brains!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:32.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, how about we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,A break...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's play WIXOSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Trash Rhino with Tawil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:48.58,Main,,0,0,0,,The Activation Ability on\NYuzuki's new LRIG is super!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki recommended\Nthat I try different cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:58.42,Main,,0,0,0,,But, none of the LRIG cards match\Nme as well as Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}did...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:10.06,Main,,0,0,0,,The world of Selector battles has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,The girls who were sealed\Ninto cards as LRIGs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,...were able to return to their former selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,"Summer's Renewal Edition"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Selector battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What was the game all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:33.17,Main,,0,0,0,,"Akira's Resolute Declaration to Blue Decks!"\NWhat was the game all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,A game that was born from the\Nhatred and sorrow of a single girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,A game of broken rules where only\Nsorrow lay in wait no matter the selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:04.24,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,...we found something within that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,"Excuse me. We can become friends--"\N...we found something within that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,We found alternatives outside the\Nrules from which to make a selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,If we didn't participate in the game,\Nwe never would have known...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,...or found what was precious to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:37.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And, I made my selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:49.04,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'll continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,...my search...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:58.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:17.06,Main,,0,0,0,,...for a yet unseen, new selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Believing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:27.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,...Ru's selection.
